item.title: CVE-2023-25768|2024-08-02T11:32:12.434Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20azure%20credentials%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Azure Credentials Plugin 253.v887e0f9e898b and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to connect to an attacker-specified web server.

item.title: CVE-2023-25766|2024-08-02T11:32:12.377Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20azure%20credentials%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Azure Credentials Plugin 253.v887e0f9e898b and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate credentials IDs of credentials stored in Jenkins.
